<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧ -<span class="c5"> بَاب:</span> الصُّلْحِ مَعَ الْمُشْرِكِينَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فِيهِ عَنْ أَبِي سُفْيَانَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[ر: ٧]</span> وَقَالَ عَوْفُ بْنُ مَالِكٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">(ثُمَّ تَكُونُ هُدْنَةٌ بَيْنَكُمْ وَبَيْنَ بَنِي الْأَصْفَرِ)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[ر: ٣٠٠٥]</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَفِيهِ سَهْلُ بْنُ حُنَيْفٍ، وَأَسْمَاءُ، وَالْمِسْوَرُ، عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[ر: ٣٠١٠، ٢٤٧٧، ٢٥٦٤]</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
